		<item>
		<title>清热解毒祛火的水果和蔬菜（夏日“清火解毒”水果排行榜！）</title>
		<link>https://www.huacao77.com/10430.html</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[广少, 腹肌之广]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Thu, 27 Jul 2023 07:34:59 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[果蔬知识]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[水果]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[清火]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[火龙果]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.huacao77.com/?p=10430</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[容易上火的小伙伴知道有什么水果是可以降火的吗？今天就来给大家盘点一下夏日最清火的水果大排名！ 清火水果NO.1 [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">容易上火的小伙伴知道有什么水果是可以降火的吗？今天就来给大家盘点一下夏日最清火的水果大排名！</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/3902b917177c863b552250fb23799bf0.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">清火水果NO.1：梨</strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">梨含水量高达84%，被称为“天然矿泉水”。中医认为梨对肺、支气管及上呼吸道有相当好的滋润功效，还可帮助消化、促进食欲。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/5fe950f4a292f00cc97e2fd76eb98a70.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">拥有这么多功效的梨足以称得上是“清火水果之王”了。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">清火水果NO.2：山竹</strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">山竹被称为“果中皇后”，性寒凉，果肉含丰富的膳食纤维、糖类、维生素及镁、钙、磷、钾等矿物元素，中医认为有清热降火、减肥润肤的功效。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/28a77e370e9bbdbab3eeb6f7adfc1ff7.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">清火水果NO.3：火龙果</strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">火龙果具有清热解毒、退肠火、通便的作用，还有益于眼睛保健、皮肤美白防黑斑。味道清甜的火龙果，是夏天不可不吃的降火佳果。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/c9c2d3a88c77275ecdea663ba2c5c120.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">清火水果NO.4：柚子</strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">柚子有“天然水果罐头”之称。中医认为，柚子果肉性凉，味甘酸，有止咳平喘、清热化痰、健脾消食的作用。它比较温和，是不错的清火水果。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/67a1c9de572f87db4c3e358ab461067e.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">清火水果NO.5：西瓜</strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">下火水果又怎能忘记夏季瓜果之王西瓜呢！中医理论认为，西瓜味甘淡、性寒，具有清热解暑、生津止渴、利尿、开胃助消化等作用，清火功能同样受到赞赏。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/3af95fe65a5d016f809b67db8dbeffd3.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">清火水果NO.6：草莓</strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">草莓酸酸甜甜，十分好吃。中医认为吃草莓可以去火、清暑、解热、除烦，所以夏天容易上火，可以选择吃草莓来降火。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/99edf55045c42014d0180c5f979feabf.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">清火水果NO.7：西红柿</strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">番茄，也叫西红柿，清热止渴，养阴凉血。也可以切片用白糖凉拌，味道酸甜可口，败火效果极佳。不过，未成熟的青色西红柿不能吃哦！</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/1e189d389a2d901c53043afda536ba72.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">清火水果NO.8：香蕉</strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">香蕉也是败火的好水果，中医认为香蕉性味甘寒微涩、无毒，具有清热止渴、清胃凉血、润肠通便、降压利尿等作用。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/222ae0a09a3e4ddcd1e8685d880e5cb5.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">清火水果NO.9：葡萄</strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">葡萄能滋养肝肾之阴分，止消渴，润筋骨，利目视，而且降火的效果不错，又能通肠胃，是暑热季节非常有益的水果。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/a6ea6cf7902f41a3dd207c8fc359487b.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">注意！</strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">寒性水果不能多吃，</strong>吃多了会因为消化不良导致腹胀。因此，肠胃功能不好的老人和孩子，不太适合吃寒凉水果。如果真的很想吃，可以在午饭后、晚饭前，少吃一点，不可过量。</p>


</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
